  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the performance of the 3M(TM) BacLite (TM) Rapid MRSA
      test system to traditional culture methods in detecting the presence of Methicillin Resistant
      Staphylococcus aureus (MRSA) directly from nasal samples.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
